House Price Prediction

Overview

This project predicts house prices based on various features such as area, number of rooms, location, and more. It uses regression techniques to understand how each feature impacts the final selling price of a property.


Objective

Build a machine learning model to predict house prices accurately.
Analyze feature importance to understand what factors influence pricing the most.
Evaluate the model using appropriate metrics like RÂ² score and MAE.

